---

<Layout
  title="Mark Amaechi — Software Developer & AI Automation Specialist"
  description="Software Developer & AI Automation Specialist based in Düsseldorf. Python, JavaScript, PHP, C++, REST APIs, AI integration. Available for hire."
>

  <!-- ═══ CANVAS BACKGROUND ═══ -->
  <canvas id="bg-canvas" class="fixed inset-0 w-full h-full -z-10 pointer-events-none"></canvas>

  <!-- ═══ NAV ═══ -->
  <nav class="fixed top-0 inset-x-0 z-50 backdrop-blur-md bg-ink-950/60 border-b border-white/5">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 md:px-10 h-16 flex items-center justify-between">
      <a href="#top" class="flex items-center gap-3 group">
        <div class="w-9 h-9 rounded-lg bg-gradient-to-br from-accent-cyan to-accent-violet flex items-center justify-center text-ink-950 font-bold text-lg">M</div>
        <span class="font-display font-semibold text-ink-50 group-hover:text-accent-cyan transition">Mark Amaechi</span>
      </a>
      <div class="hidden md:flex items-center gap-8 text-sm">
        <a href="#about" class="text-ink-300 hover:text-accent-cyan transition" data-i18n="nav.about">About</a>
        <a href="#capabilities" class="text-ink-300 hover:text-accent-cyan transition" data-i18n="nav.capabilities">Capabilities</a>
        <a href="#skills" class="text-ink-300 hover:text-accent-cyan transition" data-i18n="nav.stack">Stack</a>
        <a href="#work" class="text-ink-300 hover:text-accent-cyan transition" data-i18n="nav.work">Work</a>
        <a href="#contact" class="text-ink-300 hover:text-accent-cyan transition" data-i18n="nav.contact">Contact</a>
      </div>
      <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
        <!-- Language toggle -->
        <div class="flex items-center bg-ink-900/60 border border-white/10 rounded-full p-0.5 font-mono text-[11px]">
          <button data-lang="en" class="lang-btn px-3 py-1 rounded-full transition text-ink-400">EN</button>
          <button data-lang="de" class="lang-btn px-3 py-1 rounded-full transition text-ink-400">DE</button>
        </div>
        <a href="#contact" class="btn-secondary text-sm py-2 px-5 hidden sm:inline-flex" data-i18n="nav.cta">Let's talk</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </nav>

  <!-- ═══ HERO ═══ -->
  <section id="top" class="min-h-screen flex items-center relative overflow-hidden pt-20">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 md:px-10 w-full relative z-10">
      <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-12 gap-12 items-center">
        <!-- Left: text -->
        <div class="lg:col-span-7 order-2 lg:order-1">
          <div class="reveal mb-6">
            <span class="section-label" data-i18n="hero.label">Software Developer · AI Automation · Düsseldorf</span>
          </div>
          <h1 class="reveal font-display font-bold text-5xl md:text-7xl lg:text-[5.5rem] leading-[0.95] tracking-tight mb-8" style="transition-delay: 80ms">
            <span data-i18n="hero.title.greeting">Hi, I'm</span><br>
            <span class="text-gradient">Mark</span> —<br>
            <span data-i18n="hero.title.tagline1">I ship software</span><br>
            <span data-i18n="hero.title.tagline2">that works.</span>
          </h1>
          <p class="reveal text-ink-300 text-lg md:text-xl max-w-xl leading-relaxed mb-6" style="transition-delay: 160ms" data-i18n="hero.subtitle">
            Software Developer &amp; AI Automation Specialist based in Düsseldorf. I build
            production-grade software, integrate AI systems, and automate the work that
            slows teams down.
          </p>
          <div class="reveal mb-10 font-mono text-sm text-ink-400 flex flex-wrap gap-x-1 gap-y-1" style="transition-delay: 220ms">
            <span class="text-accent-cyan">Python</span>
            <span class="text-ink-600">·</span>
            <span>JavaScript</span>
            <span class="text-ink-600">·</span>
            <span>PHP</span>
            <span class="text-ink-600">·</span>
            <span>C++</span>
            <span class="text-ink-600">·</span>
            <span>SQL</span>
            <span class="text-ink-600">·</span>
            <span class="text-accent-violet">AI Integration</span>
          </div>
          <div class="reveal flex flex-wrap gap-4" style="transition-delay: 300ms">
            <a href="#work" class="btn-primary">
              <span data-i18n="hero.cta.work">View my work</span>
              <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2.5" d="M19 14l-7 7m0 0l-7-7m7 7V3"/></svg>
            </a>
            <a href="#contact" class="btn-secondary" data-i18n="hero.cta.contact">Get in touch</a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Right: photo with glow -->
        <div class="lg:col-span-5 order-1 lg:order-2">
          <div class="reveal relative mx-auto max-w-[340px] aspect-[2/3]" style="transition-delay: 120ms">
            <!-- Glow layers -->
            <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-accent-cyan via-accent-teal to-accent-violet rounded-[32px] blur-3xl opacity-50 animate-glow-pulse"></div>
            <div class="absolute -inset-2 bg-gradient-to-tr from-accent-violet to-accent-cyan rounded-[34px] opacity-80"></div>
            <!-- Photo -->
            <div class="relative rounded-[32px] overflow-hidden bg-ink-800 h-full shadow-2xl shadow-black/50">
              <img src="/images/mark.png" alt="Mark Amaechi" class="w-full h-full object-cover" />
              <!-- Gradient overlay -->
              <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-ink-950/60 via-transparent to-transparent"></div>
              <!-- Corner badges -->
              <div class="absolute top-4 left-4 flex items-center gap-2 glass px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full">
                <span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-green-400 animate-pulse"></span>
                <span class="text-xs font-medium text-ink-100">Available</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Scroll indicator -->
    <div class="absolute bottom-8 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 flex flex-col items-center gap-2 text-ink-400">
      <span class="text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.25em] font-mono">Scroll</span>
      <div class="w-[1px] h-8 bg-gradient-to-b from-accent-cyan to-transparent"></div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ═══ ABOUT ═══ -->
  <section id="about" class="py-32 md:py-40 relative">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 md:px-10">
      <div class="reveal mb-12">
        <span class="section-label" data-i18n="about.label">About</span>
        <h2 class="font-display font-bold text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl mt-6 leading-tight">
          <span data-i18n="about.title1">Certified developer.</span><br>
          <span class="text-gradient" data-i18n="about.title2">AI-native by practice.</span>
        </h2>
      </div>
      <div class="reveal space-y-5 text-ink-200 text-lg md:text-xl leading-relaxed" style="transition-delay: 120ms">
        <p data-i18n-html="about.p1">
          I'm a <strong class="text-ink-50">certified software developer (IHK)</strong> and AI automation
          specialist — from C++ systems programming to Python automation and JavaScript web apps.
        </p>
        <p data-i18n-html="about.p2">
          I build <strong class="text-ink-50">production-grade software</strong> — CRM systems with REST APIs,
          automated workflows and database architecture that goes from concept to deployment independently.
        </p>
        <p data-i18n-html="about.p3">
          I work daily with AI tools like <strong class="text-ink-50">Claude Code</strong> and the
          <strong class="text-ink-50"> OpenAI API</strong>, building GPT-powered automations and
          integrating LLMs into real applications.
        </p>
        <p data-i18n-html="about.p4">
          Before development, I spent three years in professional client communication — which
          means I don't just write code, I know what users are actually trying to do when they describe a problem.
        </p>
        <p class="text-accent-cyan font-mono text-base" data-i18n="about.available">
          Based in Düsseldorf. Available now.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ═══ CAPABILITIES (formerly Experience) ═══ -->
  <section id="capabilities" class="py-32 md:py-40 relative">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 md:px-10">
      <div class="reveal mb-20">
